# evaluate

## Evaluate a Model

## Description
Evaluate a model object. See implementations in the keras and tfestimators packages. 


## Usage
```r
evaluate(object, ...) 
```

## Arguments
|Arguments|Description|
|---|---|
| object | An evaluatable `R` object. |
| ... | Optional arguments passed on to implementing methods. |
